#: ui/pages/data_page.py:98
msgid ""
"Typical order: Gather → Convert → Deduplicate (optional) → Upscale "
"(optional) → Create Dataset. If class folders are already under your raw "
"data root, skip Gather and start at Convert. See docs/DATA_PIPELINE.md for "
"storage on external drives and large vs small images."
msgstr ""
"Typical order: Gather → Convert → Deduplicate (optional) → Upscale "
"(optional) → Create Dataset. If class folders are already under your raw "
"data root, skip Gather and start at Convert. See docs/DATA_PIPELINE.md for "
"storage on external drives and large vs small images."

